channel.title: Nobody can log into my server
channel.description:
I have made a server, but nobody can log into my server , i can log in with 127.0.0.1.
I have portforwarded, i did it just the same as on portforward.com, AND i have opened the port on my firewall.
My router is a sweexLW050 btw.
Please help me.
-Stig
